  ARRAY['Best rates (3.5% cash back, 2.625× travel) locked behind Preferred Rewards — requires $100,000+ in BofA/Merrill assets','Without Preferred Rewards, BofA cards are competitive but not market leaders vs. Citi Double Cash or Capital One Quicksilver at the same tier','Premium Rewards Elite ($550/year) offers fewer differentiated travel perks than Chase Sapphire Reserve at the same fee level']::text[],
  '{"cost":8.2,"features":8.4,"ux":8.6,"support":7.8}'::jsonb,
  'The best issuer for existing Bank of America customers',
