  ARRAY['Active Cash: 2% flat on everything, no tracking','Strong 0% APR on purchases & balance transfers','Autograph Journey: 3× restaurants, travel, streaming']::text[],
  ARRAY['Active Cash earns 2% flat cash rewards on every purchase with no annual fee and no categories to track — one of the simplest cards in the US market','Strong 0% APR intro periods on both new purchases and balance transfers, with no annual fee on the Active Cash','Autograph Journey ($95/year) earns 3× on restaurants, travel, and streaming with a $50 annual airline credit']::text[],
  ARRAY['Smaller card lineup than Chase or Capital One — fewer niche cards for specific spending patterns','No premium lounge access at any tier — the Autograph Journey does not include Priority Pass','2016 fake-accounts scandal is part of the brand''s history — a factor for trust-sensitive customers']::text[],
  '{"cost":8.8,"features":7.6,"ux":8.4,"support":7.2}'::jsonb,
  'The best issuer for a simple, uncomplicated flat-rate cash back card',
  'Wells Fargo''s Active Cash is one of the cleanest flat-rate cash back cards in the US market — 2% on every purchase with no rotating categories, no minimums, and the strongest 0% APR offer currently running (15 months on purchases and balance transfers, no annual fee). The Autograph Journey adds a mid-tier travel card with 3× on restaurants, travel, and streaming with a $50 airline credit. Wells Fargo''s card lineup is narrower than Chase or Capital One and lacks any dedicated premium lounge card — but for a user who wants one simple, uncomplicated card with a competitive rate, it''s hard to beat.',
  false, NULL, 'https://creditcards.wellsfargo.com/', false, 'Best for: Simple flat-rate cash back', 7,
  'https://creditcards.wellsfargo.com/', DATE '2026-07-05', true
),
